Sundial App Privacy Policy
The app uses iOS location services to calculate sun and 
moon rise/set times. The apps stores your last location
and desired alerts in the app's user preferences. These 
preferences are only stored on your iOS device and backed
up by Apple based on your iOS settings.
The app does
not
collect any other information. It does
*not* transmit your location, alert settings, or any other
piece of data to any server of any kind.
Questions? E-mail
contact@sundialapp.com
.